  <h1 class="title is-4">Application Functionality:</h1>
  <ul>
    <li>Users can browse and filter products by brand and category.</li>
    <li>
      Detailed product information, including descriptions, tags, prices, and
      images, enhances user experience and decision-making.
    </li>
    <li>
      The structured database schema supports robust querying and filtering
      capabilities, optimizing performance and user interaction.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h1 class="title is-4">Conclusion:</h1>
  <p>
    This setup not only ensures accurate categorization and brand referencing
    but also enhances user navigation and exploration of makeup products,
    leveraging a well-organized database structure and intuitive application
    design.
  </p>
</div>
